title: Rewards for 8bit LEGO competition?
body:
I was just wondering if anybody who entered the LEGO LoL comp a while ago has gotten their skins yet, I don't seem to have..
Kinda freaking like I entered my summoner-name wrong?

Thanks,
GB - Keilosophy

replies.body:
Hi Keilosophy,

I emailed you yesterday confirming that the skins are now in your inventory :)

Please login to see them.
